\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><h2 id=\"缩放\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#缩放\"><span>缩放</span></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/css/2023-07-30-15-29-37.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"language-css line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"css\" data-title=\"css\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">transform:scale(x轴缩放倍数</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">y轴缩放倍数);</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div><h2 id=\"渐变\" tabindex=\"-1\"><a class=\"header-anchor\" href=\"#渐变\"><span>渐变</span></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/css/2023-07-30-15-35-28.gif\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<div class=\"language-css line-numbers-mode\" data-ext=\"css\" data-title=\"css\"><button class=\"copy\" title=\"复制代码\" data-copied=\"已复制\"></button><pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark vp-code\" v-pre=\"\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#1E754F;--shiki-dark:#4D9375\">background-image</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">:linear-gradient(颜色1 位置</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">,</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">颜色2 位置2);</span></span></code></pre>\n\n<div class=\"line-numbers\" aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"counter-reset:line-number 0\"><div class=\"line-number\"></div></div></div>","tagOpen":"<template>","tagClose":"</template>"},"script":null,"scriptSetup":null,"scripts":[],"styles":[],"customBlocks":[]},"content":"![](/body/green_6.webp)\n\n## 字体图标\n\n- iconfront\n\n- Fontawesome\n- ……\n\n## 位移\n\n![](/css/2023-07-30-14-54-42.gif)\n### 语法\n\n```css\ntransform:translate(水平移动距离,垂直移动距离);\n```\n\n### 取值\n\n- 像素单位数值\n- 百分比(参照物为盒子自身尺寸)\n\n### 技巧\n\n::: warning\n\ntranslate()如果只给出`一个值`，表示`x轴`方向移动距离\n\n:::\n\n::: tip\n单独设置某个方向的移动距离:`translateX()`/`translateY()`\n加入`transition:all`，动画过渡更加丝滑\n\n:::\n\n## 旋转\n\n### 平面旋转\n![](/css/2023-07-30-15-20-29.gif)\n\n\n#### 语法\n```css\ntransform：rotate(角度deg);\n```\n#### 取值\n取值为`正`，则`顺`时针旋转\n取值为`负`，则`逆`时针旋转\n\n### 转换原点\n![](/css/2023-07-30-15-25-12.gif)\n#### 语法\n\n```css\ntransform-origin:原点水平位置,原点垂直位置;\n```\n\n#### 取值\n\n- 方位名词(left、top、right、bottom、center)\n- 像素单位数值\n- 百分比(参照盒子自身尺寸计算)\n\n### 多重转换\n![](/css/2023-07-30-15-27-54.gif)\n\n#### 语法\n\n```css\ntransform:translate() rotate();\n```\n\n## 缩放\n![](/css/2023-07-30-15-29-37.gif)\n```css\ntransform:scale(x轴缩放倍数,y轴缩放倍数);\n```\n\n## 渐变\n\n![](/css/2023-07-30-15-35-28.gif)\n```css\nbackground-image:linear-gradient(颜色1 位置,颜色2 位置2);\n```","excerpt":"","tasklists":0,"title":"","headers":[{"level":2,"title":"字体图标","slug":"字体图标","link":"#字体图标","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"位移","slug":"位移","link":"#位移","children":[{"level":3,"title":"语法","slug":"语法","link":"#语法","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"取值","slug":"取值","link":"#取值","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"技巧","slug":"技巧","link":"#技巧","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"旋转","slug":"旋转","link":"#旋转","children":[{"level":3,"title":"平面旋转","slug":"平面旋转","link":"#平面旋转","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"转换原点","slug":"转换原点","link":"#转换原点","children":[]},{"level":3,"title":"多重转换","slug":"多重转换","link":"#多重转换","children":[]}]},{"level":2,"title":"缩放","slug":"缩放","link":"#缩放","children":[]},{"level":2,"title":"渐变","slug":"渐变","link":"#渐变","children":[]}]}}
